    "article": "<p><strong>Miniblog</strong> is an opinionated and extremely minimal blogging template built with <a href=\"https://astro.build/\">Astro</a> and <a href=\"https://tailwindcss.com/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Tailwind CSS</a>, heavily inspired by <a href=\"https://jrmyphlmn.com/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">jrmyphlmn.com</a>.</p><ul><li>Blog post authoring using <a href=\"https://www.markdownguide.org/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Markdown</a> and <a href=\"https://mdxjs.com/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">MDX</a> for component-style content</li><li>Code block syntax highlighting with <a href=\"https://github.com/shikijs/shiki\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Shiki</a></li><li><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/RSS\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">RSS</a> feed and sitemap generation</li><li>SEO optimization, with customizable OpenGraph image support</li><li>Code formatting with <a href=\"https://prettier.io/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Prettier</a></li></ul><p><br/></p>",
